text: Luis Eduardo Vélez Sánchez (born 26 July 1986) is an archer from Mexico. Vélez competed at the 2008 Summer Olympics and the 2012 Summer Olympics.Luis Eduardo Vélez == References == Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:Mexican archers Category:Olympians for Mexico Category:Sportspeople from Guadalajara, Jalisco
